{"tid":1563518,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"再修訂版 Glory be to Thee, Hong Kong 國歌歌詞","createTime":"2019-09-12T12:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T17:13:44.000Z","uid":321405,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"93248d17f5833173be94c09584d432199b436136","tid":1563518,"uid":321405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:15:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">《願榮光歸香港》</span></span></strong><br />\n曲: thomas dgx yhl<br />\n詞（中文）: t, 眾連登仔 <br />\n原詞（英文）: 七劍浣春秋 (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547782/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547782/page/1</a>)<br />\n主要係想capture番中文歌詞原本既意思，尤其是係 &ldquo;何以&rdquo; 呢兩隻字。<br />\n同埋希望會好唱小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Glory be to Hong Kong</strong></span></span></em><br />\n<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">How came tears to flow o&rsquo;er this land?</span><br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">How came fear to shackle our hands?</span><br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Hold high your heads! Let our cries be heard</span><br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Till the day our freedom comes</span><br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">For what in our hearts burns this rage? </span><br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">For what, undaunted, do we keep our faith?</span><br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Our blood be on us, march on, we shall fight</span><br />\n建自由 光輝 香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Till the day our freedom comes</span><br />\n<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">When our eyes no longer see,</span><br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">In the dark, the horn of conscience calls us forth </span><br />\n&quot;捍自由 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">To liberty,</span><br />\n來齊集這裡 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Hand in hand</span><br />\n來全力抗對<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">To the very end</span><br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅&quot;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">With hope, with song, and dignity!</span><br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">The People shall rise, Day will break, We&rsquo;ll be free.</span><br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Brothers and Sisters, Revolution of Our Times! </span><br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">May Liberty thrive and our Rights divine,</span><br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!</span>"},{"pid":"50fc77dbf856a22ea33cac68c03c5f9696ee012c","tid":1563518,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:15:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"435145a02f46ad028adfeb05170e07597d6e4461","tid":1563518,"uid":207898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"好嘢黎"},{"pid":"cde60c1ed4b5b00eade12b7527b80f38649a8071","tid":1563518,"uid":207898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:38: